{"tid":1088600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"脫歐變脫衣 14名環保團體示威者闖入下議院脫衣抗議","createTime":"2019-04-02T07:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T08:27:18.000Z","uid":75969,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3a95ecff979161f8a1cf1c0b2a30c985748f4f59","tid":1088600,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190402/640_fee8452d31ebe2cfc5b77a550d767390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190402%2F640_fee8452d31ebe2cfc5b77a550d767390.jpg&h=294ff4a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國下議院今日討論脫歐議案，就在議員們發言辯論期間，突然有抗議團體闖入，並脫下衣服展示口號，當場脫歐議程變脫衣抗議，工黨議員米利班(Ed Miliband)更是看到脫窗。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日電訊報》報導，英國下議院今日再度為脫歐協議案進行辯論，正當議員們進行辯論程序時，突然在2樓旁聽席出現一陣騷動。原來是環保團體「反抗滅絕」(Extinction Rebellion)亂入，現場有14成員突然脫衣，秀出寫在身上的口號，包括「SOS」和「停止浪費時間」，還有示威者用膠水把雙手黏在玻璃上。最後有警衛出動，將抗議人士帶出議會。<br />\n<br />\n「反抗滅絕」的騷動驚動了1樓議員，但每一位議員的反應大不同，有的議員拿起手機拍照記錄，但像米利班則是看到一度雙眼「脫窗」，兩個眼珠子瞪到好似要從眼窩中掉出來。<br />\n<br />\n「反抗滅絕」其中一名35歲成員、也是前老師歐福蘭德(Mark &Oslash;vland)就說，有許多重要的議題，常常被政府與媒體忽視，所以只好用這種強迫的方式，吸引大家注意。另外一名68歲成員班尼斯(Oliver Baines)更說：「我們沒有時間等待了！」他稱如果政府沒有作為，未來將會陷入水深火熱之中。<br />\n<br />\n「反抗滅絕」團體在去年10月成立，關注全球暖化議題，該團體更相信所謂的「12年大限」，因為先前聯合國報告指出，地球最快會在2030年左右突破攝氏1.5度的「升溫大限」，全球氣候變遷將會陷入一場災難。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190402/640_873c166c90601b4048de1953bfa7a4f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190402%2F640_873c166c90601b4048de1953bfa7a4f1.jpg&h=f63d2218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190402/640_53d8a90bfcc2604877d3bfc617deac77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190402%2F640_53d8a90bfcc2604877d3bfc617deac77.jpg&h=f9ce58f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190402/640_f62e298a62764e10416d3e669431853b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190402%2F640_f62e298a62764e10416d3e669431853b.jpg&h=515c50a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190402/1543851/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190402%2F1543851%2F&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m6z%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=b91544e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190402%2F1543851%2F&h=8217d359\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190402/1543851/</a>"},{"pid":"bd4c800c6a4883a15e81c14c5e8dace3d3dc7e70","tid":1088600,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5cc759e4c978eece2c1e8d9b668b2505f74b2c","tid":1088600,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:42:24.000Z","msg":"gay test..."},{"pid":"5db9802aede2dcd80959069caf33cf68c227981c","tid":1088600,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:51:30.000Z","msg":"半裸女 bam得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b51e2f8628a500d4806f24f88c90639527a9cd","tid":1088600,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:53:43.000Z","msg":"Attention whores"},{"pid":"af8625b50b105a9db3d8ea2e00733e90f46b12ce","tid":1088600,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T08:02:39.000Z","msg":"最右邊有個未除褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5cc5fa470e40930d9cfada3ed055e5e444761c2","tid":1088600,"uid":155177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim